-- Santander U.K. Set Aside $1.2 Billion on PPI Last Year
-- B y   G a v i n   F i n c h
-- 2012-08-31T06:59:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-31/santander-u-k-set-aside-1-2-billion-on-ppi-last-year-correct-.html
(Corrects to show the provision was for the first half of
2011.)  Santander U.K. set aside 731 million
pounds ($1.2 billion) for customer remediation in the first half
of 2011, “principally” in relation to the mis-selling of
payment protection insurance, the firm said in a statement
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gavin Finch in London at 
